{"word":"H204 - אֹון - ʼÔwn - one - On","slug":"H204","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אֹון</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʼÔwn"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>one"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>On"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>אן און</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>'ôn 'ôn</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>one</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> On = \"strength or vigour\" <ol><li>city in lower Egypt, bordering land of Goshen, centre of sun-worship, residence of Potipherah (priest of On and father-in-law of Joseph)</li></ol> <p />Origin: of Egyptian derivation <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Location "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H201\">H201</a>, <a href=\"#/H3982\">H3982</a>, <a href=\"#/H534\">H534</a>, <a href=\"#/H559\">H559</a>, <a href=\"#/H561\">H561</a>, <a href=\"#/H562\">H562</a>, <a href=\"#/H564\">H564</a>, <a href=\"#/H565\">H565</a>, <a href=\"#/H566\">H566</a>, <a href=\"#/H567\">H567</a>, <a href=\"#/H568\">H568</a>, <a href=\"#/H569\">H569</a>, <a href=\"#/H570\">H570</a>, <a href=\"#/H577\">H577</a>"}]}